data.description: Come take a look inside this Spacious home on the corner lot! Open Kitchen and living room layout. Inside large kitchen you will find a double pantry and plenty of cabinet space. A split bedroom floorplan allows for maximum privacy in the Master bedroom, where relaxing is easy in the Garden tub. EcoWater Systems water softener that provides filtered water throughout the home as well as reverse osmosis water in the kitchen. This home also includes a security system with Doorbell Camera previously monitored through ADT and a sprinkler system. Finally, the large 2 car garage has plenty of space for cars and storage.
